Dear Student,

The IC & SR, in its efforts to encourage and enable the spirit of innovatio
n within the IIT Madras Innovation Ecosystem,  has created a provision to p
rovide support to immediately graduating students.  This is to encourage th
e student to complete, or bring to the next logical step, any projects/inno
vation that he has undertaken during his tenure within IIT Madras.  This su
pport is limited to a period of 6 months.  The support is at the level of a
 Project Associate.

Desirous Students are requested to apply by filling up the form:



The last date for applying for this is 31st Aug 2016.

Please make the best use of this opportunity. For additional information, p
lease feel free to contact either Prof. Mahesh Panchagnula (mvp@iitm.ac.in)
 or Prof. Ashwin Mahalingam (mash@iitm.ac.in).



DEAN, IC & SR



